Package org.jmlspecs.jmlunitng.strategy

Interface Summary
Strategy The interface for all test data generation strategies.
 

Class Summary
ArrayStrategy The strategy for all array types.
BooleanStrategy The default strategy for the boolean type.
ByteStrategy The default strategy for the byte type.
CharStrategy The default strategy for the char type.
DoubleStrategy The default strategy for the double type.
FloatStrategy The default strategy for the float type.
IntStrategy The default strategy for the int type.
LongStrategy The default strategy for the long type.
NonPrimitiveStrategy The parent strategy for all non-primitive types.
ObjectStrategy The strategy for all non-primitive, non-array types.
PrimitiveStrategy The basic framework of a primitive test data generation strategy.
ShortStrategy The default strategy for the short type.
StringStrategy The default strategy for type java.lang.String, which - although an object - is treated as primitive by JMLUnitNG.
